        </a>
        <a href="/professional-services" class="btn btn-outline">
          <span>Explore Career Services</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-visual reveal-scale delay-2">
      <img class="hero-logo-large" src="/images/mawingu-logo.png" alt="Mawingu HR Solutions Logo">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-scroll-hint reveal-up delay-5" aria-hidden="true">
    <span>Scroll to explore</span>
    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Reality of Scaling Section -->
<section class="section section-reality">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="split-layout">
      <div class="split-left">
        <span class="section-label reveal-up">The Challenge</span>
        <h2 class="section-title reveal-up delay-1">The Reality<br>of Scaling</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle reveal-up delay-2">Growth exposes people gaps.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="split-right">
        <div class="reality-card reveal-right delay-1">
          <h3>When HR is informal:</h3>
          <ul class="reality-list">
            <li class="reveal-right delay-2">
              <span class="reality-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-coral)" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
              </span>
              Leaders spend time resolving conflict instead of driving strategy
            </li>
            <li class="reveal-right delay-3">
              <span class="reality-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-coral)" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
              </span>
              Hiring becomes reactive
            </li>
            <li class="reveal-right delay-4">
              <span class="reality-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-coral)" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
              </span>
              Compliance risks increase
            </li>
            <li class="reveal-right delay-5">
              <span class="reality-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-coral)" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
              </span>
              Performance lacks accountability
            </li>
            <li class="reveal-right delay-6">
              <span class="reality-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-coral)" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
              </span>
              Culture weakens
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="reality-resolution reveal-up delay-3">
          <blockquote>
            <p>HR is not administration.<br><strong>It is operational infrastructure.</strong></p>
          </blockquote>
          <p class="resolution-text">Mawingu builds that infrastructure.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

